    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Well, it seems that it never really was an option per se. It's an object on the instantsearch instance that we can mutate in order to configure the template system. That doesn't like the best API we can provide :/\r\n\r\nOne key point here, is that we may not want to keep template mechanics in the long term. This means that adding this option in the parameters will mean that we need to remove it eventually... ",
